---
const upgrades = [
  { name: "Museos Vaticanos, Capilla Sixtina y Basílica de San Pedro", price: "$2,800 MXN", image: "/images/vaticano.webp" },
  { name: "Paseo en Góndola, Murano y Burano", price: "$2,250 MXN", image: "/images/venecia.webp" },
  { name: "Innsbruck (Valle del Tirol y Swarovski)", price: "$1,900 MXN", image: "/images/innsbruck.webp" },
  { name: "Castillo de Heidelberg", price: "$1,250 MXN", image: "/images/heidelberg.webp" },
  { name: "Londres Histórico (Museo Británico, Támesis y London Eye)", price: "$3,450 MXN", image: "/images/bigben.webp" },
  { name: "Instagram desde París con Crucero Panorámico", price: "$2,100 MXN", image: "/images/arco-triunfo.webp" },
  { name: "Los Secretos del Palacio de Versalles y Barrio Latino", price: "$2,450 MXN", image: "/images/versalles.webp" }
];
---
<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">HAZ TU VIAJE TODAVÍA MÁS TUYO</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Estas experiencias no están incluidas en el paquete básico y requieren reserva anticipada.</p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
      {upgrades.map(item => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 group flex flex-col">
          <!-- Image Container -->
          <div class="h-56 overflow-hidden relative">
            {item.image ? (
              <img src={item.image} alt={item.name} class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" />
            ) : (
              <div class="w-full h-full bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-amber-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
              </div>
            )}
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-amber-800 font-bold shadow-sm">
              {item.price}
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-snug">
              {item.name}
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="mt-16 text-gray-400 text-sm italic">
      Nota: Los precios en pesos son informativos y calculados bajo el tipo de cambio vigente al momento de su liquidación.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
